This paper is about algorithm selection in the field of evolutionary computation, specifically for the CMA-ES algorithm. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with optimization problems, which could place it in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. The paper also involves data analysis and experimentation, which could place it in the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with adaptive systems, which could place it in the cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-category.
